MASTER AGENT ORCHESTRATION

OVERVIEW

The Master Agent Orchestration Agent acts as the central coordinator for the entire healthcare solution. It receives all user requests, understands the user's intent, and routes the conversation to the most appropriate specialized agent. The goal is to ensure that each query is handled by the right expert agent while maintaining a seamless user experience.

The following specialized agents are orchestrated through the Master Agent:

• Health Assistant Agent

• Appointment Booking Agent

• Risk Analysis Agent

• Medication Adherence Agent

• Doctor Recommendation Agent

• General Support Agent

---

AGENT ROUTING AND CONTEXT TRANSFER

The Master Agent uses AgentScript routing and Utilis.Transition to transfer the complete conversation context between agents.

During agent handoff, the following information is preserved:

• User query

• Conversation history

• User intent

• Previous agent responses

• Session context

This ensures that users do not need to repeat information when the conversation is routed from one agent to another.

