WEBSITE INTEGRATION

The complete solution is connected to the healthcare Experience Cloud website using:

• Enhanced Messaging Channel

• Embedded Service Deployment

• Agentforce Service Agent

. Omni flow for Service Agent (for this agent)

When a user opens the website and starts a chat, the request is sent to the Master Agent. The Master Agent then identifies the intent and routes the request to the appropriate specialized agent while preserving the complete conversation context.

---

EXPECTED OUTCOME

The Master Agent provides intelligent agent orchestration across all healthcare agents. Through AgentScript routing and Utilis.Transition context passing, the system enables seamless Agent-to-Agent communication, maintains conversation continuity, and ensures that every user request is handled by the most suitable specialized agent.
